# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

Resource for managing LDAP database configuration in the Janssen Server.
This resource allows you to configure external LDAP servers for user authentication and data storage.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "jans_ldap_database_configuration" "example" {
  config_id         = "auth_ldap_server"
  local_primary_key = "uid"
  primary_key       = "uid"
  max_connections   = 200
  servers           = ["ldap.example.com:1636"]
  use_ssl           = true
  bind_dn           = "cn=directory manager"
  bind_password     = "your-secure-password"
  base_dns          = ["ou=people,o=jans"]

  lifecycle {
    ignore_changes = [bind_password]
  }
}
```

